    "7423230": {
      "title": "Estimation of synthetic accessibility score of drug-like molecules based on molecular complexity and fragment contributions",
      "abstract": "Background ::: A method to estimate ease of synthesis (synthetic accessibility) of drug-like molecules is needed in many areas of the drug discovery process. The development and validation of such a method that is able to characterize molecule synthetic accessibility as a score between 1 (easy to make) and 10 (very difficult to make) is described in this article."
